As experts in FPC, we assist you in making informed decisions on FPC design, manufacturing and assembly. Transferring circuit schematic into routing design can be a challenging process. With a dedicated team of design engineers, we are able to deliver innovative design solutions.

Cadence design system.

CAD/CAM-empowered DFM platform.

Proven track record of New Product Introduction (NPI).

R&D collaboration with University Sains Malaysia (USM) and University of Southampton.

Graduate engineers from USM, Imperial College London and University of Cambridge.

In-house artwork plotter for non-disclosure protection.

CAD/CAM design platform guarantees accuracy and speed up New Product Introduction (NPI).
